NVision Task 

to build project you must have:
* java version > 8
* gradle version > 4

build command:
./build.bat

run command:
./start.bat

test section:
to add entities

curl -X POST \
  http://127.0.0.1:8080/jobs \
  -H 'Content-Type: application/xml' \
  -H 'cache-control: no-cache' \
  -d '<jobs>
    <job id="3">
        <type>t</type>
        <user>user</user>
        <device>dev1</device>
        <amount>12</amount>
    </job>
    <job id="2">
        <type>2t</type>
        <user>u3ser</user>
        <device>dev2</device>
        <amount>212</amount>
    </job>
    <job id="1">
        <type>2t—É</type>
        <user>user2</user>
        <device>dev1</device>
        <amount>212</amount>
    </job>
</jobs>'

to do search:

curl -X GET \
  'http://127.0.0.1:8080/statistics?user=user&device=dev1' \
  -H 'Content-Type: application/xml' \
  -H 'cache-control: no-cache'
